      "id": 11530,
      "name": "app4g",
      "username": "app4g",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/6a8cbe/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2022-11-17T08:43:56.565Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi There,</p>\n<p>I don\u2019t have a device that supports Stage Manager and I do not (yet) have the latest Xcode w/ simulator that supports iPadOS 16.1 to test my app. (Mine is currently on 16.0 and seems like it doesn\u2019t support stage manager)</p>\n<p>Doing some quick research on stackoverflow / youtube / apple developer forums, I can\u2019t seem to find what is the minimum size that a window can be resized to.</p>\n<p>A typical website from safari, I think it\u2019s possible that it be resized down to Stock Ticker size (can you confirm?), but other apps installed on the iPad are just normal typical non-website types which has a (somewhat) predefined layout.</p>\n<p>Example App below on the iPad and during split view, the conditions are such that when the width &gt; height or vice-versa then the app will automatically switch from landscape view to like Portrait view.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/d/daf582cae21547ffe4bb550cad481b511e6f9540.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/daf582cae21547ffe4bb550cad481b511e6f9540\" title=\"Simulator Screen Shot - iPad Pro (12.9-inch) (5th generation) - 2022-11-17 at 16.29.00\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/daf582cae21547ffe4bb550cad481b511e6f9540_2_333x250.jpeg\" alt=\"Simulator Screen Shot - iPad Pro (12.9-inch) (5th generation) - 2022-11-17 at 16.29.00\" data-base62-sha1=\"vf05MsMnSSAdQcKwrJobu2DSTRe\" width=\"333\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/daf582cae21547ffe4bb550cad481b511e6f9540_2_333x250.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/daf582cae21547ffe4bb550cad481b511e6f9540_2_499x375.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/daf582cae21547ffe4bb550cad481b511e6f9540_2_666x500.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/daf582cae21547ffe4bb550cad481b511e6f9540_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Simulator Screen Shot - iPad Pro (12.9-inch) (5th generation) - 2022-11-17 at 16.29.00</span><span class=\"informations\">2732\u00d72048 870 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/7/796be19671402a8cf4b69402182e1153d98d7c90.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/796be19671402a8cf4b69402182e1153d98d7c90\" title=\"Simulator Screen Shot - iPad Pro (12.9-inch) (5th generation) - 2022-11-17 at 16.30.28\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/796be19671402a8cf4b69402182e1153d98d7c90_2_333x250.jpeg\" alt=\"Simulator Screen Shot - iPad Pro (12.9-inch) (5th generation) - 2022-11-17 at 16.30.28\" data-base62-sha1=\"hk8UjDfjX7UfWSIcVEAwHEcd3H2\" width=\"333\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/796be19671402a8cf4b69402182e1153d98d7c90_2_333x250.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/796be19671402a8cf4b69402182e1153d98d7c90_2_499x375.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/796be19671402a8cf4b69402182e1153d98d7c90_2_666x500.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/796be19671402a8cf4b69402182e1153d98d7c90_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Simulator Screen Shot - iPad Pro (12.9-inch) (5th generation) - 2022-11-17 at 16.30.28</span><span class=\"informations\">2732\u00d72048 818 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Thus far, I\u2019ve not seen any reference/youtube about apps being able to be minimised down to Stock Ticker Size. (I\u2019m presuming that you meant a size that is like the iPad dock?)</p>\n<p>Regarding screen brightness. I\u2019m not entirely sure that we can dim the brightness programatically only for the app. The setting i\u2019ve found is that it will just adjust the phone/tablet\u2019s native brightness (down to 0) which will affect all apps running at the moment.</p>\n<p>Have you tried this option in Settings-&gt;General-&gt;Accessibility-&gt;Reduce White Point? I find that this helps to reduce the intensity of the \u201cwhite\u201d colours which is basically the text on screen.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/b/b7575bde8292e839ca3d1f4b704d5727046e0ead.png\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/b7575bde8292e839ca3d1f4b704d5727046e0ead\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b7575bde8292e839ca3d1f4b704d5727046e0ead_2_209x375.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"q9UxDJAYTOXOIjZLKT94nVQIcB7\" width=\"209\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b7575bde8292e839ca3d1f4b704d5727046e0ead_2_209x375.png, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b7575bde8292e839ca3d1f4b704d5727046e0ead_2_313x562.png 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b7575bde8292e839ca3d1f4b704d5727046e0ead_2_418x750.png 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b7575bde8292e839ca3d1f4b704d5727046e0ead_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1170\u00d72096 320 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
